  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK726">
<l>vāḷoṭeṉ vaṉkaṇṇa rallārkku nūloṭe </l>
<l>ṉuṇṇavai yañcu pavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What have they to do with a sword who are not valiant, or they with learning who are afraid of an intelligent assembly ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
